<p>Hello,</p>
<p>I recently uploaded a picture to <a href="QR_decomposition" title="QR decomposition">QR decomposition</a>. I had created it with <a href="Inkspace" title="Inkspace" class="mw-redirect">Inkspace</a> and it looked fine on my machine, but it's messed up on the website. You can look at <a href="User_talk_Bruguiea#Image_added_at_QR_decomposition" title="User talk:Bruguiea">my talk page</a> to see the list of problems. I posted more information on <a href="../User_talk_Joel_B._Lewis#QR_decomposition" title="User talk:Joel B. Lewis">User_talk:Joel_B._Lewis#QR_decomposition</a>.</p>
